<h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 16px;">Verify Your Email Address</h1>

<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;">
    Hi <%= user.username %>,
</p>

<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px;">
    Thank you for registering with StreamVista! To complete your registration and start using your account, please verify your email address.
</p>

<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;">
    Click the button below to verify your email address:
</p>

<a href="<%= baseUrl %>/users/verify/<%= verificationToken %>" class="button">
    Verify Email Address
</a>

<div style="margin: 24px 0; padding: 16px; background-color: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 6px;">
    <p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
        If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
        <span style="color: #4f46e5;"><%= baseUrl %>/users/verify/<%= verificationToken %></span>
    </p>
</div>

<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
    This verification link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.
</p>

<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 24px;">
    If you didn't create an account with StreamVista, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
    Best regards,<br>
    The StreamVista Team
</p> 